<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Baking Organizer - Add New</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Add New Recipe</h1>
    <nav class="top-nav">
      <a href="/" class="home-btn">üè† Home</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="add-post-form">
      <h2>Upload Recipe Details</h2>
      <p><strong>Heuristic Note:</strong> Text file processing takes approx. 2 seconds. (IH#2)</p>
      
      <form id="uploadForm">
        <label for="recipeFile">Choose Recipe Text File (.txt):</label>
        <input type="file" id="recipeFile" accept=".txt" required>
        
        <label for="recipeImage" style="margin-top: 15px; display: block;">Upload Finished Product Photo:</label>
        <input type="file" id="recipeImage" accept="image/*">
        
        <div class="form-actions" style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 20px;">
          <button type="submit" id="addBtn">Add to Collection</button>
          <button type="button" id="cancelBtn" onclick="window.location.href='/'" style="background: #bbb; color: white;">Cancel</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #fff8e1; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #ffe082;">
      <h3>How to format your .txt file (IH#1)</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
        Line 1: Name <br>
        Line 2: Price (e.g. 10.00) <br>
        Line 3: Ingredients (separated by commas) <br>
        Line 4+: Instructions/Steps
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>